4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to become specialists in the field. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes each week with a maximum of 16 participants per class. Students will build foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Participants will learn about data loss prevention and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. More details can be found at [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop